  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284">
        <l>eñcuporuṭ kiḷavi ceñco lāyiṟ</l>
        <l>piṟpaṭak kiḷavār muṟpaṭak kiḷattal.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/172/mode/1up">172</ref>.</p>
      <p>
urai: eñcuporuṭ kiḷavi eṉpatu ― eccavummai eṉṟavāṟu; ceñ col āyiṉ eṉpatu ― cevveṇṇāyiṉ eṉṟavāṟu; piṟpaṭak kiḷavār muṟpaṭak kiḷattal eṉpatu ― kālamuṉṉākac collār iṭamuṉṉākac colluvār eṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘aṭakupulāl pāku pāḷitamu muṇṇāṉ</l>
        <l>kaṭalpōluṅ kalvi yavaṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpataṉuḷ, aṭaku pulāl pāku eṉṟu cevveṇṇālē eṇṇip, piṉṉaip pāḷitamum eṉṟu eccavummaiyai iṭamuṉṉākki vaittu eṇṇiṉavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka. (36)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n222/mode/1up">219</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n223/mode/1up">220</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. eccavummaiyāṟṟaḻuvappaṭum eñcuporuṭkiḷavi ummaiyil collāyiṉ, avvummaiyil collai avvummaittoṭarkkup piṉ collātu muṉ colluka e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u - m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Cena-cit1">
        <l>cāttaṉ vantāṉ koṟṟaṉum vantāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Cena-cit2">
        <l>koṟṟaṉum vantāṉ cāttaṉ vantāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉap piṟpaṭak kiḷappiṉ, muṟkūṟiyataṉai vilakkuvatupōṉṟu poruḷ koḷḷāmai kaṇṭukoḷka.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Cena-cit3">
        <l>‘aṭaku pulālpāku pāḷitamu muṇṇāṉ―</l>
        <l>kaṭalpōluṅ kalvi yavaṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉpatumatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Cena-cit4">
        <l>ummaiyaṭātē tāṉē niṟṟaliṟ ceñcol</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟār.
      </p>
      <p>
ceñcolāyiṉ muṟpaṭakkiḷakkaveṉavē, eñcuporuṭkiḷavi ummaiyoṭu variṟ piṟpaṭakkiḷakkaveṉṟavāṟām.	(36)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/310/mode/1up">310</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ecca ummai niṟṟaṟkuriya iṭam
      </p>
      <lg>
        <l>eñcuporuṭ kiḷavi ceñ<sic>cō</sic> lāyiṟ</l>
        <l>piṟpaṭak kiḷavār muṟpaṭak kiḷattal.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
iḵtu, ecca vummaikkaṇ collutal vakaimai kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) eñcu poruṭkiḷavi ― eccavummaiyāṟṟaḻuvappaṭumeñcu poruṭ kiḷavi, ceñcolāyiṉ piṟpaṭak kiḷavār muṟpaṭak kiḷattal ― ummaiyil collāyiṉ, avvummaiyil collai yavvummait toṭarkkup piṉcollātu muṉ colluka veṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>cāttaṉ vantāṉ koṟṟaṉum vantāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘aṭaku pulāl pāku pāḷitamu muṇṇāṉ.</l>
        <l>‘kaṭal pōluṅ kalvi yavaṉ.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum. piṟpaṭak kiḷappiṉ poruḷ koḷḷāmai kāṇka. ceñcolāyiṉ muṟpaṭak kiḷakka, veṉavē yummaiyōṭu variṉ <sic>yi</sic>ṟpaṭak kiḷakka veṉṟavāṟām.  <num xml:lang="en">(36)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n189/mode/1up">182</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ecca ummaikkaṇ vaḻūukkāttalai uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
i-ḷ: ― eñcu poruṭkiḷavi, ummaiyil collāyiṉ, ummai, varukiṉṟa collōṭu kiḷakka. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
        u-m:―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Tey-cit1">
        <l>cāttaṉum vantāṉ, koṟṟaṉum varum</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉṟaṟpālataṉkaṇ ōr ummaivaril,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC284-Tey-cit2">
        <l>cāttaṉ vantāṉ, koṟṟaṉum varum</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉka.	[35]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
